		}
		{
			dependencies: ["369A9E51C5A05AB7"]
			description: ["Andesite Casings are structural components for many Create machines. Craft them by right-clicking an Andesite Alloy onto a log in the world. They are a prerequisite for the Mechanical Press and most other early machines — stockpile them before you need them."]
