		{
			dependencies: ["378C3A0358FD2ABD"]
			description: ["Rose Quartz is found underground near Diorite. Polish it using Sandpaper (crafted from Rose Quartz itself — use the first piece to make the tool) to produce Polished Rose Quartz, a critical component in Electron Tubes and advanced precision parts."]
