			description: ["Electron Tubes are precision components assembled from Iron, Polished Rose Quartz, and Copper. They are required for the Deployer, Mechanical Arm, and Precision Mechanism — three of Create's most powerful automation tools. Mass-produce them early; demand only grows."]
