			description: ["The Deployer holds any tool or item and activates it against blocks directly in front of it, powered by rotational input. It can place blocks, use items on surfaces, till soil, or even attack mobs. Combined with a Mechanical Arm and a Sequenced Gearshift, it enables fully automated crafting lines."]
